description:
On today’s show, Emily along with Producer Jamie are talking about why sex is important beyond just bringing you pleasure.

They discuss why one out of five women say they’re unsatisfied with their sex life, ways to go about inviting a friend to join a threesome, and why no orgasm is inferior to another – just as long as you get there. Plus, the importance of speaking up about likes and dislikes in the bedroom – from sex acts to frequency.
